libhydrogen
------------------------------------------
The Hydrogen library is a small, easy-to-use, hard-to-misuse cryptographic
library.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libhydrogen-devel-0+git20240510-1bl1
  libhydrogen0-0+git20240510-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  ninja-1.12.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/jedisct1/libhydrogen

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/jedisct1/libhydrogen.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libhydrogen-0+git20240510-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libhydrogen-0+git20240510-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libhydrogen-0+git20240510-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhydrogen-0+git20240510-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhydrogen0-0+git20240510-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libhydrogen-devel-0+git20240510-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libhydrogen)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libhydrogen.README
  /usr/share/doc/libhydrogen/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libhydrogen/README.md

(libhydrogen0)
  /usr/bin/cyghydrogen-0.dll

(libhydrogen-devel)
  /usr/include/hydrogen.h
  /usr/lib/cmake/hydrogen/hydrogen-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/hydrogen/hydrogen-targets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/hydrogen/hydrogen-targets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libhydrogen.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libhydrogen.pc

------------------

